        default <T extends EObject> void modify(java.util.function.Function<BusinessObjectContext,T> bocToBoToModifyMapper,
                                        java.util.function.BiConsumer<T,BusinessObjectContext> modifier)
        Calls the specified modifier for each business object provided by the bocToBoToModifyMapper. Also provides the business object context. The business objects contained in the business object context must not be modified.
        Parameters:
        bocToBoToModifyMapper - is a function which returns the object which should be modified based on a business object context.
        modifier - is a function which is passed the object to be modified and the business object context.
